data.description: Charming little home on Elm St. Beautiful back yard, this property was very well taken care of and was left in great condition by its last owners. Beautiful tile floors, carpet was left in great condition, only thing that needs to be done is some interior paint touch up. Great house at a fantastic price. Don't wait around to look at this, it won't be here long.
